  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND CHAPTER 944, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2010, AS LAST AMENDED BY CHAPTER 909, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2022, TO EXTEND THE DATE OF REPEAL FROM JULY 1, 2026,  TO JULY 1, 2030, ON THE PROVISION OF LAW THAT AUTHORIZES THE TOWN OF BYHALIA, MISSISSIPPI, TO IMPOSE A TAX AT A RATE NOT TO EXCEED 2% UPON THE GROSS PROCEEDS OF ROOM RENTALS FOR HOTELS OR MOTELS IN THE TOWN; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
